v 3
d 'kmplot': Publication-Ready Kaplan-Meier Plots for Stata
d
d One-command publication-quality Kaplan-Meier survival curves
d and cumulative incidence plots. Supports confidence bands,
d number-at-risk tables, median survival lines, censoring marks,
d log-rank p-values, and colorblind-safe styling.
d
d Requires: Stata version 16+
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260315
d License: MIT
d
d Author: Timothy P Copeland
d Department of Clinical Neuroscience, Karolinska Institutet
d
d KW: Kaplan-Meier
d KW: survival curves
d KW: cumulative incidence
d KW: risk table
d KW: publication
d
f kmplot.ado
f kmplot.sthlp
f _kmplot_risktable.ado
